To deploy mc-operator in self-hosted:

    $ ./hack/deploy/setup.sh --docker-registry=<docker-registry-name>
or, $ ./hack/deploy/setup.sh --docker-registry=<docker-registry-name> --selfhosted

To run mc-operator in local machine to connect minikube:

    $ ./hack/deploy/setup.sh --minikube

To uninstall:

    $ ./hack/deploy/setup.sh --uninstall (--purge)

() -> Optional
